Requirements List - GlobalMart

Functional Requirements

ID: FR1
Requirement: User Registration
Description: Users can create account with email/phone

ID: FR2
Requirement: User Login
Description: Users can log in with credentials

ID: FR3
Requirement: Browse Products
Description: Users can view products by category

ID: FR4
Requirement: Product Search
Description: Users can search for products by keyword

ID: FR5
Requirement: Multi-currency Display
Description: Products show prices in selected currency

ID: FR6
Requirement: Shopping Cart
Description: Users can add/remove items from cart

ID: FR7
Requirement: Wishlist
Description: Users can save products to wishlist

ID: FR8
Requirement: Price Comparison
Description: Users can compare prices across sellers

ID: FR9
Requirement: Checkout
Description: Users can proceed to checkout with cart items

ID: FR10
Requirement: Payment Simulation
Description: Users can simulate payment (no real money)

ID: FR11
Requirement: Order History
Description: Users can view past orders

ID: FR12
Requirement: Logistics Tracking
Description: Users can track shipping status

ID: FR13
Requirement: User Reviews
Description: Users can leave product reviews

ID: FR14
Requirement: Seller Information
Description: Users can view seller details and ratings

ID: FR15
Requirement: Language Toggle
Description: Users can switch between English and Chinese

Non-Functional Requirements

ID: NFR1
Requirement: Performance
Description: Page load time under 3 seconds

ID: NFR2
Requirement: Usability
Description: Interface must be intuitive for international users

ID: NFR3
Requirement: Security
Description: User data encrypted; secure login

ID: NFR4
Requirement: Reliability
Description: System uptime 99%

ID: NFR5
Requirement: Scalability
Description: Should handle up to 1000 concurrent users

ID: NFR6
Requirement: Compatibility
Description: Works on Chrome, Firefox, Safari

ID: NFR7
Requirement: Maintainability
Description: Code should be modular and well-documented
